Fantastic game!!!! This reminded me of another game that you made called Kloki I think. I love how you come up with constantly different ways of keeping the player guessing. You also have a very intuitive way of training the player to play the game without clunky instructions that get in the way. I would absolutely love to see more variations of your games. I would love to see a sequel to your game HOOK. Keep making games like this please!

One of the prettiest/cleanest and awesomest puzzle game out there. I can imagine some people would feel upset about the lack of tutorials but that's actually part of the experience. IRL I like to play with mechanical puzzles that you have to take apart. I thought this was a really fun and relaxing game and it reminded me of those - gave me the same feeling as when I sit and fiddle with interlocking pieces of metal and eventually feel great when I get them apart. You can't really fail and you just keep puzzling at a level until you succeed which makes it really chill. A great bedtime game.

Instead games nowadays make you grind for no reason!

I think it's worth the price, especially without ads.
